        \hat O\!\!\left[\prod_{i>n}^N\prod_{k=1}^{\textrm{length}}
        e^{-ia_{ik}H_k\Delta t}\right]\!\!\!
        \left[\prod_{k=j}^{\textrm{length}}
        e^{-ia_{nk}H_k\Delta t}\right]\!H_j\!\!
        \left[\prod_{k=0}^{j-1}
